line_1: An' fleeching chiels around her thrang,
line_2: Till she miskens her a' day lang.

line_1: IT was on a morn, when we were thrang,
line_2: When ane at the door chapp't loud and lang.
Wi' sweet-milk-cheese, in monie a whang,

line_1: To sway out-owre the feather'd thrang,
line_2: Who dread his martial bill and fang:
"God save the King" 's a cukoo sang
